snippet.title: Saindhav Trailer - Telugu | Venkatesh Daggubati | Sailesh Kolanu | Niharika Entertainment |
snippet.description:
Watch the Telugu Trailer of Victory #VenkateshDaggubati’s highly anticipated Landmark 75th film #SAINDHAV 

IN CINEMAS FOR SANKRANTHI ON JANUARY 13th!!

SAINDHAV is an upcoming New Age Action Film Starring Venkatesh Daggubati in the Lead Role, Co-starring Baby Ssara Palekar, Nawazuddin Siddiqui, Arya, Shraddha Srinath, Ruhani Sharma, Andrea Jeremiah. Written & Directed By Dr. Sailesh Kolanu. Music by Santhosh  Narayanan, DOP by S.Manikandan, Editing by Garry Bh, Produced by Venkat Boyanapalli On Niharika Entertainment banner. Worldwide Releasing in theatres for Sankranthi on Jan 13th, 2024.

Cast - Venkatesh Daggubati , Baby Ssara Palekar, Nawazuddin Siddiqui, Arya, Shraddha Srinath, Ruhani Sharma, Andrea Jeremiah, Jisshu sen gupta, Mukesh Rishi, JP, Getup Srinu and others…

snippet.description:

snippet.title: Reality Of BIG BOSS - Aishwariya's Untold Stories on Bharti TV
snippet.description:
🎙️ Brace yourselves for the most candid, unfiltered episode yet on Bharti TV! Join the laughter riot as the dynamic comedy couple, Bharti and Harsh, sit down with the recently eliminated Big Boss contestant, Aishwariya, for a no-holds-barred conversation on all things Big Boss.😂 Get ready for a rollercoaster of emotions and laughter as Aishwariya spills the beans on her rollercoaster journey inside the Big Boss house. From the dramatic confrontations to the hilarious behind-the-scenes antics, this podcast is your backstage pass to the real world of Big Boss. 👀 Tune in to witness Aishwariya's journey like never before, as Bharti and Harsh add their unique comedic flair to the narrative. Subscribe now and get ready for a hilarious, eye-opening ride through the ups and downs of the Big Boss house.🎉 Don't miss out on the fun – hit that subscribe button, grab your popcorn, and join Bharti and Harsh as they bring you the unfiltered reality of Big Boss, one laugh at a time! 🌈

snippet.title: PREGNANCY പഠിപ്പിച്ച വലിയ പാഠം | @dimplerose4417 | Josh Talks Malayalam
snippet.description:
#joshtalksmalayalam #dimplerose #motherhood #womenempowerment 

പഠിച്ചുകൊണ്ട് വളരൂ ജോഷ് Talks-ലൂടെ- നിങ്ങളുടെ Communication Skills മെച്ചപ്പെടുത്താൻ, ജോഷ് ടോക്സിന്റെ Malayalam to English app-ൽ ചേരുക: https://bit.ly/JoshTalksMalayalamToEnglish

ഡിംപിൾ റോസ് @dimplerose4417  എന്ന ARTIST -നെ സിനിമകളിലൂടെയും സീരിയലുകളിലൂടെയും ഒരുപാട് മലയാളികൾക്ക് പരിചിതയായ മുഖമാണ്. ഒരു ബാലതാരമായി തുടങ്ങി,  പ്രധാന വേഷങ്ങൾ ചെയ്യുന്നതുവരെ, ഡിംപിൾ വീട്ടിലെ ഒരു അംഗമെന്നോണം എല്ലാവര്ക്കും പ്രിയപ്പെട്ടവളായി. എന്നിരുന്നാലും, ജീവിതത്തിന്റെ ഒരു ഘട്ടത്തിൽ ഡിംപിളിന് എന്ത് സംഭവിച്ചുവെന്ന് പലർക്കും അറിയുമായിരിക്കില്ല? ഈ #joshtalks -ൽ, തന്റെ ഗർഭകാലത്തെ ഹൃദയഭേദകമായ അനുഭവം ഡിംപിൾ പങ്കുവെക്കുന്നു. നമ്മുടെ സമൂഹത്തിലെ പല സ്ത്രീകളും നേരിടുന്ന പ്രയാസങ്ങളെ ഡിംപിൾ തന്റെ ടോൾകിലൂടെ അവതരിപ്പിക്കുന്നു. താൻ അനുഭവിച്ച ജീവിതത്തിന്റെ ഏറ്റവും ദുഷ്‌കരമായ അവസ്ഥയിൽ നിന്ന് പാഠങ്ങൾ ഉൾക്കൊണ്ട് തനിക്കുണ്ടായ സ്വയം പരിവർത്തനത്തെക്കുറിച്ചും ഡിംപിൾ പറയുന്നു. ഡിംപിളിനെപ്പോലെ നമുക്കുനേരെ വരുന്ന വെല്ലുവിളികളെ നമ്മുടെ താഴ്ച്ചയും ഉയർച്ചയും മനസ്സിലാക്കാനും അതിനനുസരിച്ച് പ്രവർത്തിക്കാനുമുള്ള അവസരമായി കാണണം. 

Dimple Rose @dimplerose4417  is a much familiar face to a lot of Malayali's for her presence in #movie and #serial . From a child artist to doing main roles, Dimple has been a like a close member in many households. However, many people don't know about what happened to Dimple at one point of her life? In her #joshtalks , she shares the heart wrenching experience of her #pregnancyjourney .Many women in our society face a lot of things that Dimple conveys in her talk. She also talks about the #selftransformation  that she had after this #pregnancy  by taking the #learnings from the toughest situation life put her in. Like Dimple, we also should see the challenges thrown to us as an opportunity to understand our lows and highs and work accordingly.

ഇപ്പോൾ നിങ്ങൾക്ക് Josh Talks വീഡിയോകളിൽ നിങ്ങളുടെ ബ്രാൻഡ് പ്രദർശിപ്പിക്കാനും പരസ്യം ചെയ്യാനും varun@joshtalks.com- ഇൽ Connect ചെയ്യൂ.

If you find this talk helpful, please like and share it and let us know in the comments box.
You can now showcase and advertise your brand on the Josh Talks videos, reach out to us at varun@joshtalks.com, if you are interested.

Josh Talks passionately believes that a well-told story has the power to reshape attitudes, lives, and ultimately, the world. We are on a mission to find and showcase the best motivational stories from across India through documented videos and live events held all over the country. Josh Talks Malayalam caters to the Malayalam speaking audience worldwide. It aims to inspire and motivate Malayali's by showcasing Malayalam motivation through the experiences of fellow Malayali's. Josh talks Malayalam and brings to you the best Malayalam motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 9 languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the setbacks they face in their career and helping them discover their true calling in life.

ജോഷ് Talks ഇന്ത്യയിലെ ഏറ്റവും പ്രേരണാത്മകമായ കഥകൾ ശേഖരിക്കുകയും അവ പങ്കുവെക്കാൻ ഒരു വേദി നൽകുകയും ചെയ്യുന്നു. വിവിധ പശ്ചാത്തലങ്ങളിൽ നിന്നുള്ള അനുഭവസ്ഥർ, അവരുടെ സംഘർഷഭരിത കഥകൾ പങ്കുവയ്ക്കുന്നു. ചെറുതായി തുടങ്ങിയ ജോഷ് Talks, നിലവിൽ 9 ഭാഷകളിൽ കഥകൾ പങ്കുവയ്ക്കുന്നു. ഊർജ്ജസ്വലരായ യുവജനങ്ങളുടെ കഴിവുകളെ പ്രോത്സാഹിപ്പിക്കുകയും, അവരുടെ ജീവിതത്തിൽ  നേരിടുന്ന തിരിച്ചടികൾ മറികടക്കാൻ അവർക്ക് പ്രചോദനം നൽകുകയും ചെയ്യുക എന്നതാണ് ഞങ്ങളുടെ ലക്ഷ്യം.
#joshtalks #deliverystory #mother #baby  #family

ജോഷ് Talks ഇന്ത്യയിലെ ഏറ്റവും പ്രേരണാത്മകമായ കഥകൾ ശേഖരിക്കുകയും അവ പങ്കുവെക്കാൻ ഒരു വേദി നൽകുകയും ചെയ്യുന്നു. വിവിധ പശ്ചാത്തലങ്ങളിൽ നിന്നുള്ള അനുഭവസ്ഥർ, അവരുടെ സംഘർഷഭരിത കഥകൾ പങ്കുവയ്ക്കുന്നു. ചെറുതായി തുടങ്ങിയ ജോഷ് Talks, നിലവിൽ 9 ഭാഷകളിൽ കഥകൾ പങ്കുവയ്ക്കുന്നു. ഊർജ്ജസ്വലരായ യുവജനങ്ങളുടെ കഴിവുകളെ പ്രോത്സാഹിപ്പിക്കുകയും, അവരുടെ ജീവിതത്തിൽ  നേരിടുന്ന തിരിച്ചടികൾ മറികടക്കാൻ അവർക്ക് പ്രചോദനം നൽകുകയും ചെയ്യുക എന്നതാണ് ഞങ്ങളുടെ ലക്ഷ്യം.

Bawri suggests a creative way for everyone to express their feelings about the gifts. The person with the least-liked gift will be subject to a fine.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 3970 - Iyer Nahi Hain Gift Se Khush?! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | तारक मेहता
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Watch the full episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSKo8X_EiY0WewaBlNt49g3

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
Navina Wadekar / Monika Bhadoriya as Bawri

Produced By: Neela Asit Modi, Asit Kumarr Modi 
Special Thanks: Mahesh Vakil, Indu Tarak Mehta

snippet.description:

Audio Credits -

Pyaar tera sanu mil jana rabb di khas neyamat ae
Tenu ek gal kehni ae tenu ek gal kehni ae
Man ja na man adiye
Tere ton rakheya hona chann da na chann adiye Tere
ton rakheya hona chann da na chann adiye Tere ton
rakheya hona
Naina da rang kala rakhna bullan da rang laal houga
Eh vi jad rabb socheya hona pakka tere naal houga
Vahle sohne phullan di
Vahle sohne phullan di akad de bhan adiye
Tere ton rakheya hona chann da na chann adiye Tere
ton rakheya hona chann da na chann adiye Tere ton
rakheya hona
Rukda mein sma dekheya lokan ne ghadi dekhi ae Aj
tak mein sunya hi si pehli war pari dekhi ae Rukda
mein sma dekheya lokan ne ghadi dekhi ae Aj tak
mein sunya hi si pehli war pari dekhi ae Lagda punjab
ch guneya
Lagda punjab ch guneya tera tan-man adiye Tere ton
rakheya hona chann da na chann adiye Tere ton
rakheya hona chann da na chann adiye Tere ton

snippet.title: Adani-Hindenburg Verdict Today. Supreme Court Pronounces Verdict
snippet.description:
#supremecourt #adanigroups #gautamadani #adanipower #hindenburg 
The Supreme Court announces its decision on petitions investigating stock price manipulation allegations against the Adani group. The verdict is delivered by Chief Justice DY Chandrachud and justices JB Pardiwala and Manoj Misra at 10:30 am on Wednesday, addressing four petitions. The judgement comes after the bench had reserved its decision on November 24.

snippet.title: Japan: Tsunami hits after series of powerful earthquakes
snippet.description:
Residents of seven Japanese regions have been urged to flee an oncoming tsunami after a series of powerful earthquakes struck the east Asian country.

A one-metre tsunami has already struck parts of the west coast along the Sea of Japan after a series of more than 20 earthquakes with a magnitude of four or stronger started shortly after 3pm local time (6am GMT).

A larger second tsunami is expected and the Japan Meteorological Agency has warned that waves as high as five metres could strike Ishikawa, one of the affected regions.

Tsunami warnings are in place for the entire length of Japan’s northern coast, running some 1,650 miles from Wakkanai in the far north of Hokkaido to Kyushu in the south.

Warnings have also been issued in Russia’s far eastern island of Sakhalin and city of Vladivostok, as well as South Korea’s Gangwon province. The tsunami waves are not expected to be large enough to endanger life.

People living in coastal areas of seven prefectures were instructed to evacuate to higher ground or to seek refuge on higher floors of sturdy buildings.

Fumio Kishida, the prime minister, has urged authorities to prioritise “human life above all else” and “spare no effort in our emergency disaster responses”.

Read the latest here: https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2024/01/01/japan-earthquake-tsunami-live-latest-damage/

snippet.title: Truckers Protest New Law That Increases Jail Term For Road Accidents
snippet.description:
A change in the colonial-era criminal laws increasing jail term in hit-and-run cases has triggered truckers' protests across the country. Under the new law, drivers can be jailed for up to 10 years for fleeing and not reporting a fatal accident. Earlier, the accused could be jailed only for up to two years under Section 304A of the IPC (causing death by negligence).

snippet.title: Trailer: Shri Swapankumarer Badami Hyenar Kobole | Abir, Paran | In Cinemas 12 Jan | hoichoi studios
snippet.description:
কলকাতা শহরে বাদামী হায়না আসছে, শুধু এইটুকু জানা গেছে যে এটা একটা বিপজ্জনক গ্যাং। আর এর হাত থেকে বাঁচতে বাঙালিকে ফিরতে হবে শ্রীস্বপনকুমারের বটতলার ডিটেক্টিভের কাছে, বাঙালিকে ফিরতে হবে দীপক চ্যাটার্জীর কাছে!

Kolkata is in danger. Word is that an evil force called Badami Hyena has the city's doom on its mind. Dipak Chatterjee, the long-forgotten detective created by pulp-fiction writer Shri Swapankumar, comes out of his web of hurt pride to save the city on his creator's insistence. But Swapankumar soon charts a crazy narrative that complicates Dipak's fate! Can the madcap detective stand victorious in the face of unprecedented danger?

#ShriSwapankumarerBadamiHyenarKobole: Official Trailer | Film directed by Debaloy Bhattacharya releases in cinemas on 12th January.

Cast: Abir Chatterjee, Paran Bandopadhaya, Shruti Das and Pratik Dutta
Director: Debaloy Bhattacharya
Story, Screenplay & Dialogues: Debaloy Bhattacharya 
DOP: Ramyadip Saha
Edit: Sanglap Bhowmik 
Music & Background Score: Amit Chatterjee
Sound Design & Mix: Anindit Roy and Adeep Singh Manki
Production House: hoichoi studios
Line Producer: Maansi Entertainment Studio

Mannat Murad Episode 29 - [Eng Sub] - Iqra Aziz - Talha Chahour - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 2nd January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Mannat Murad Digitally Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Mannat is a beautiful young girl who hails from a progressive family that values love, care, and mutual respect. Raised in an environment where everyone's choices are respected, Mannat enjoys the freedom to make her own decisions. Following the untimely demise of her parents, she finds support from her elder brother, Nafees, who showers her with affection.

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Khumar Episode 11 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Feroze Khan - Neelam Muneer - 29th December 2023 - Har Pal Geo

Khumar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

Khumar is a timeless love story that delves into the challenges arising from societal class differences and the negativity that stems from them. Khumar explores the complexities of love in the face of societal expectations and challenges. Faiz and Hareem, two individuals from different backgrounds, find their lives connected by destiny.

Faiz, born into an affluent family, contrasts sharply with Hareem, who hails from a
lower-middle-class background. Despite their differences, fate weaves their paths together. Hareem, diligently working to make ends meet amid her brother Rufi's educational needs and her mother's medical expenses, faces numerous hurdles. In the midst of her struggles, Faiz, a friend of Rufi's, silently supports them financially and even gets work for Hareem, albeit discreetly.

Hareem's family doesn't know that Faiz loves her, leading to a one-sided love affair. Faiz's love for Hareem remains a secret, but his mother disapproves of his association with Hareem's family due to the significant class difference. But fate decides to play its tune, and an unexpected event turns the lives of Faiz and Hareem upside down.

What was this surprising turn of events that changed everything for Faiz and Hareem? Will the gap in their social status keep them apart? Can Faiz convince his mother to accept Hareem? If they marry, can they create a happy life together despite their different backgrounds and mindsets?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation 
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi 
Writer: Maha Malik
Director: Ali Faizan

snippet.title: Tsunami warning in Japan after strong earthquake | BBC News
snippet.description:
Japan has issued a major tsunami warning after a 7.6 magnitude earthquake struck the central region.
 
Residents in the coastal Noto area in Ishikawa prefecture were asked to "evacuate immediately to higher ground," national broadcaster NHK said.
 
Authorities have warned of waves as high as 5m in Noto.
 
They also issued tsunami warnings for neighbouring Niigata and Toyama prefectures, where they said waves could reach 3m.
 
Public television flashed "EVACUATE" in big letters, urging residents to flee to higher ground despite the winter weather.

Subscribe here: http://bit.ly/1rbfUog

For more news, analysis and features visit: www.bbc.com/news 

#Japan #Earthquake #BBCNews

Episode 3969: Santa Collects Gifts
--------------------------------------------------------
Nattu Kaka and Bagha disguise themselves as Santa Claus and collect everyone's gifts. All of the Gokuldham residents follow the guidelines by wrapping their gifts in red paper. Tapu has delegated the task of present collection to Nattu Kaka and Bagha, allowing him to relax at home. Later, Jetha attempts to subtly test his gift. Finally, Gokuldham gets decked up for the Christmas festivities.

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Mannat Murad Episode 28 - [Eng Sub] - Iqra Aziz - Talha Chahour - Digitally Presented by PEL - 1st January 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Mannat Murad Digitally Presented by PEL

Mannat is a beautiful young girl who hails from a progressive family that values love, care, and mutual respect. Raised in an environment where everyone's choices are respected, Mannat enjoys the freedom to make her own decisions. Following the untimely demise of her parents, she finds support from her elder brother, Nafees, who showers her with affection.

On the other hand, Murad belongs to a conservative family where his mother, the matriarch, wields significant influence over his life choices. As the only son, Murad is burdened with the responsibility of fulfilling his family's expectations. Soft-spoken and romantic by nature, Murad finds himself unable to defy his mother's authority, especially after the passing of his father.

Despite their starkly contrasting backgrounds, Mannat and Murad's hearts find solace in each other's presence, and they fall deeply in love. However, their families' interference creates misunderstandings between Mannat and Murad, testing the strength of their bond.

Will their families agree to their union? Will Mannat's family, with their open-mindedness, find common ground with Murad's conservative household? Can Mannat and Murad's love for each other withstand the motives of their families, who seek to create further misunderstandings between them?

snippet.description:

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada

snippet.description:
Hi RJ Sha Family, Its been shocking to hear the news that Captain vijayakanth is no more. However, there are some important aspects about Vijayakanth that everyone should keep in mind. In the late 2000s, children primarily associated Vijayakanth with meme content. Nevertheless, this video will undoubtedly highlight the most commendable actions and deeds of Vijayakanth.

#captainvijayakanth #vijayakanth #rjsha #shaboothree 

****************************************

snippet.description:
7 years after the blockbuster hit Kirik Party, we invite you to the craziest party in town - on the 26th of Jan, 2024. 

‘Warning song’ from the film Bachelor Party is an Upbeat Party Number dedicated to all the married men out there. The Bachelors sympathize with you, empathize with you and wanna party with you. Get your dancing shoes on and thump the play button.

#EeSalaPartyJoru

Music: Arjun Ramu
Singer: Vijay Prakash

ದೊಡ್ಡೋರೆಲ್ಲಾ ಹೇಳೋ ಮಾತಿಗೆ ತಲೆಬಾಗಿ, ಫೋಟೋ  ನೋಡಿ ಹುಡುಗಿ ಬಣ್ಣಕೆ ಬೆರಗಾಗಿ

ಮದುವೆ ಯಾವಾಗಂತ ಕೇಳೋ ನೆಂಟರಿಗೆಲ್ಲಾ, ತಾಂಬೂಲ ಹಂಚುವಂತ ಟೈಮು ಬಂತಲ್ಲ

ಹಂಗಂದುಕೊಂಡು ಮನಸ್ಸಿನಲ್ಲೇ ತಿಂದು ಮಂಡಿಗೆ, ನೀ ಸಿಲ್ಕು ಪಂಚೆ ಹಾಕಿಕೊಂಡು ಬಿದ್ದೆ ಗುಂಡಿಗೆ

ಆ ಕಾಶಿಯಾತ್ರೆ STOP ಮಾಡೋ ಸೋದರ ಮಾವನ್ನ, IGNORE ಮಾಡಿ ಓಡಿ ಹೋಗು ಕೇಳೋ ಮಾತನ್ನ...

ಬ್ಯಾಡವೋ ಮಗನೆ ನೂರು ಥರದ ಸ್ಕ್ಯಾಮು ಮದುವೆ, ಪಾಪ ಹುಡುಗರನು DAILY ಸುಡುವ ಸ್ಕೀಮು ಮದುವೆ 

ಊಟಿಗೆ ಹೋಗಿ ಮಧುಚಂದ್ರ ಮುಗಿಸಿ, 
ಇಷ್ಟೇನಾ ಜೀವ್ನ ಅಂತ ನಿಂಗೆ ಅನಿಸಿ.
ನೊಂದ ಮನಸಿಗೆ ಹೇಳಿ ಸಮಾಧಾನ, 
ಅಮ್ಮೋರ ಗಂಡನೆಂಬ ಕೀರ್ತಿಗಳಿಸಿ.
ಮಗುವಾದರೆ ಎಲ್ಲಾ ತೊಂದರೆ, 
ಸರಿ ಹೋಗಬಹುದು ಎಂದುಕೊಂಡು ಲೈಟು ಆರಿಸಿ 

ಸಂಸಾರವೆಂಬ TV ಮುಂದೆ ಕೈಯ್ಯ ಕಟ್ಟುವೆ, ನಿನ್ ಹೆಂಡ್ತಿ ಹಾಕಿದ ಚಾನಲ್ಲನ್ನೇ DAILY ನೋಡುವೆ

ನಡು ರಾತ್ರಿಯಲ್ಲಿ ಏಳಬೇಕು ಪಾಪು ಅತ್ತರೆ, ಅದರಂಡು ನೀನೆ ತೊಳೆಯಬೇಕು ಅಯ್ಯೋ ದೇವರೇ

ಬ್ಯಾಡವೋ ಮಗನೆ ನೂರು ಥರದ ಸ್ಕ್ಯಾಮು ಮದುವೆ... ನಾಲ್ಕು ದಿನ ನಗಿಸಿ ಮುಗಿಸೆ ಬಿಡುವ ಸ್ಕೀಮು ಮದುವೆ!

snippet.title: 'Rock/Roman Kahani Shuru🤯' The Rock RETURNS on Raw, Jinder Mahal - WWE Raw Highlights 2024 Day 1
snippet.description:
Topics Covered In Video-
1) WWE Raw 1 January 2024 highlights & full show results in Hindi
2) WWE Day 1 2024 highlights
3) The Rock returns to WWE Raw Day 1 episode
4) The Rock & Jinder Mahal full segment
5) The Rock challenges Roman Reigns referring Head of the Table
6) Seth Rollins Vs Drew McIntyre WWE World Heavyweight Championship

#wweraw #therock #romanreigns #wwe

'Rock/Roman Kahani Shuru🤯' The Rock RETURNS on Raw, Jinder Mahal - WWE Raw Highlights 2024 Day 1

Witness the thrilling WWE RAW highlights from January 1, 2024, featuring the electrifying return of The Rock! The Brahma Bull made a stunning comeback on RAW, setting the stage for an epic showdown against Jinder Mahal. This jaw-dropping segment between The Rock and Jinder Mahal captivated audiences, promising an intense battle to come. Alongside this momentous return, Roman Reigns also made headlines, hinting at a potential clash with The Rock at WWE Day 1 2024. Stay updated on all the latest WWE RAW news, highlights, and much more, now available in Hindi for a wider audience to enjoy the adrenaline-pumping action of the wrestling world.
The Becky Lynch vs. Nia Jax match was an intense back-and-forth encounter where both competitors displayed their athleticism and resilience. Throughout the bout, they exchanged a flurry of strikes, signature moves, and powerful slams. The match showcased a series of impactful moments with Becky trying to counter Nia's dominant offense. Despite Becky's relentless attacks, Nia Jax proved to be a formidable opponent, ultimately securing the win via Pinfall with The Annihilator.
Cody Rhodes took to the ring to address Shinsuke Nakamura, expressing his frustration with Nakamura's actions and challenging him to end their feud that night. Nakamura responded cryptically, hinting at a continuation of their conflict.
Miz TV featured The Judgment Day faction, led by R-Truth, where a confrontation unfolded between them and Cody Rhodes and Shinsuke Nakamura. The tensions led to a tag team match announcement, reuniting Awesome Truth against members of The Judgment Day.
In the ensuing bout, The Awesome Truth triumphed over The Judgment Day in a hard-fought match showcasing thrilling back-and-forth action.
The WWE Women's World Championship match between Rhea Ripley and Ivy Nile, accompanied by The Creed Brothers, was a hard-hitting clash. Ultimately, Ripley retained her title via Pinfall with The Rip Tide after a fiercely contested battle.
The electrifying return of CM Punk was announced for the upcoming episode of Raw, generating significant anticipation. Following that, The Rock made a surprise appearance to confront Jinder Mahal, leading to a heated verbal exchange and a physical altercation between the two superstars.
Natalya and Tegan Nox faced Shayna Baszler and Zoey Stark in a tag team match, where Baszler and Stark secured the victory via Pinfall after a well-fought battle.
Further, a WWE 2024 Preview Special was announced to air on Peacock, featuring notable superstars and a major announcement from Triple H. Additionally, matches for the next Raw episode were confirmed, including Cody Rhodes taking on Shinsuke Nakamura and a Women's Tag Team Title defense.
The main event for the night saw Seth Rollins defending the WWE World Heavyweight Championship against Drew McIntyre. The match was a display of physicality and resilience, with Rollins ultimately retaining the title after a hard-fought battle against McIntyre.

Stay updated on all the latest WWE RAW news, highlights, and much more, now available in Hindi for a wider audience to enjoy the adrenaline-pumping action of the wrestling world.
The Becky Lynch vs. Nia Jax match was an intense back-and-forth encounter where both competitors displayed their athleticism and resilience. Throughout the bout, they exchanged a flurry of strikes, signature moves, and powerful slams. The match showcased a series of impactful moments with Becky trying to counter Nia's dominant offense. Despite Becky's relentless attacks, Nia Jax proved to be a formidable opponent, ultimately securing the win via Pinfall with The Annihilator.
Cody Rhodes took to the ring to address Shinsuke Nakamura, expressing his frustration with Nakamura's actions and challenging him to end their feud that night. Nakamura responded cryptically, hinting at a continuation of their conflict.
Miz TV featured The Judgment Day faction, led by R-Truth, where a confrontation unfolded between them and Cody Rhodes and Shinsuke Nakamura. The tensions led to a tag team match announcement, reuniting Awesome Truth against members of The Judgment Day.
In the ensuing bout, The Awesome Truth triumphed over The Judgment Day in a hard-fought match showcasing thrilling back-and-forth action.
The WWE Women's World Championship match between Rhea Ripley and Ivy Nile, accompanied by The Creed Brothers, was a hard-hitting clash. Ultimately, Ripley retained her title via Pinfall with The Rip Tide after a fiercely contested battle.
The electrifying return of CM Punk was announced for the upcoming episode of Raw, generating significant anticipation. Following that, The Rock made a surprise appearance to confront Jinder Mahal, leading to a heated verbal exchange and a physical altercation between the two superstars.
Natalya and Tegan Nox faced Shayna Baszler and Zoey Stark in a tag team match, where Baszler and Stark secured the victory via Pinfall after a well-fought battle.
Further, a WWE 2024 Preview Special was announced to air on Peacock, featuring notable superstars and a major announcement from Triple H. Additionally, matches for the next Raw episode were confirmed, including Cody Rhodes taking on Shinsuke Nakamura and a Women's Tag Team Title defense.
The main event for the night saw Seth Rollins defending the WWE World Heavyweight Championship against Drew McIntyre. The match was a display of physicality and resilience, with Rollins ultimately retaining the title after a hard-fought battle against McIntyre.

snippet.title: LIVE: Prime Minister Narendra Modi's massive roadshow in Ayodhya
snippet.description:
Ahead of the launch of development projects, Ayodhya Dham Junction Railway Station and Ayodhya Airport, Prime Minister Narendra Modi held a enormous roadshow in Ayodhya Dham, UP. With this the Pran-Pratishtha of Shri Ram Temple will be held on January 22nd, 2024.
